'''胡桃派'''是以[[玉米糖漿|玉米糖漿]]和[[碧根果|美國山核桃]]製成的甜[[西式餡餅|派]]，是[[美國南方飲食|美國南方美食]]，亦常見於節慶佳餚。它一般加入鹽和香草作調味<ref>[http://busycooks.about.com/od/sweetpierecipes/r/bestpecanpie.htm Best Pecan Pie]</ref>，[[巧克力|巧克力]]和[[波本威士忌|波本威士忌]]也是很受歡迎的新興食材<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cooks.com/rec/search/0,1-00,bourbon_pecan_pie,FF.html |title=Cooks.com Bourbon Pecan Pie Recipes |accessdate=2011-10-21 |archive-date=2018-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823110719/https://www.cooks.com/rec/search/0,1-00,bourbon_pecan_pie,FF.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。食用時也可以在派上添加[[生奶油|生奶油]]<ref>[http://www.countryliving.com/recipefinder/pecan-pie-bourbon-whipped-cream-3020 Pecan Pie with Bourbon Whipped Cream]</ref>。

